tas_df <- readRDS("../Ex1_whoiswho/Ex1_tas_df.rds")
# Downscaling
X <- tas_df[, "ERA5"]
Y <- tas_df[, "GHCND_orly"]
ina <- is.na(X) | is.na(Y)
X <- X[!ina]
Y <- Y[!ina]
dates <- as.numeric(rownames(tas_df))
dates <- dates[!ina]

Sparation en base d'apprentissage et base de test (calibration/validation)

iapp <- dates < 20000101
X_app <- X[iapp]
Y_app <- Y[iapp]
X_test <- X[!iapp]
Y_test <- Y[!iapp]

  inn <- which.min(dist)
